    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/261">Chuonradus</persName> divina providente misericordia
                        Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Imperatoriae
                        maiestatis sublimitas quanto alcius extollitur, tanto humilius peticionibus
                        fidelium adquiescere debet, maxime cum ipsa petitio ad illius servicium
                        pertinere cognoscitur, cuius gloriosissimo munere eandem peticionem
                        adimplendi possibilitatem recepimus. Idcirco omnium catholice fidei
                        nostrorumque fidelium noverit universitas, qualiter ob interventum et
                        exaudibiles preces Kadelohi episcopi nostrique fidelissimi cancellarii atque
                            <persName key="#Archbishops" ref="#people/1590">Geboardi</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/594"><orgName key="#Churches"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/1471">Ravenne</orgName></placeName> nostri
                        dilecti <rs key="#Archbishops">archiepiscopi</rs>
                        <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574">Vuidonem</persName> venerabilem
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Exemption #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">sancte Dei genitricis Marie constructi in
                                <rs key="#Islands">insula</rs> que vocatur <placeName key="#Islands"
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName> ipsumque
                        monasterium cum eadem insula Pomposia omnemque eiusdem monasterii
                        pertinenciam sub nostri <rs key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >mundiburdii</rs> et imperialis regiminis defensione gratanter
                        recipimus. Insuper concedimus predicto abbati Vuidoni eiusque predicto
                        monasterio Pomposie nostri precepti largitionem confirmantes eidem sancto ac
                        venerabili loco nostra imperiali auctoritate omnes res et possessiones eius
                        mobiles et immobiles iuste ac legaliter sibi pertinentes. Quibus itaque
                        generaliter confirmatis, futuras insidiancium occasiones timentes
                        specialiter predicto monasterio Pomposie tam ipsam insulam Pomposiam ex
                        integro quam extra eandem insulam, scilicet <geogName ref="#estates/2454"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/3559">Lacum Sanctum</placeName></geogName>,
                        in <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs> vero <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2449"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/485"
                                >Comaclense</placeName></geogName> et <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/84"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/80"
                                >Ferariense</placeName></geogName> et <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2435"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3538"
                                >Gavellense</placeName></geogName> seu <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2423"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/594"
                                >[R]avennate</placeName></geogName> sive <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2458"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3513"
                                >Faventino</placeName></geogName> atque <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2409"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3512"
                                >Corniliense</placeName></geogName> et <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2459"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3515"
                                >Liviense</placeName></geogName>, <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/2480"><placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/4602"
                                >Pupiliense</placeName></geogName> autem et <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1479"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/1890">Cescenate</placeName></geogName> necnon <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1480"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/1806">Ariminense</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2371"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/1812">Orbino</placeName></geogName> vero et <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/1481"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/1803">Castello Felicitatis</placeName></geogName> atque
                            <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2462"><placeName
                                key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/2752">Perusino</placeName></geogName>,
                        sive quicquid presentaliter in <rs key="#Islands">insula</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Islands" ref="#places/4652">Salti</placeName> tenere
                        videtur, nominatim vero terram que prenominato monasterio Pomposie ex
                        iudicatu <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchionis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke"><name ref="Hugo">Ugonis</name></persName>
                        evenit, videlicet <placeName ref="#places/4653">Soleriam</placeName> et
                            <placeName ref="#places/4654">Cavallariam</placeName> ac <placeName
                            ref="#places/4655">Polixinum</placeName> atque in comitatu Ferariense et
                        Gavellense firmissima et preceptali corroboracione confirmamus. Liceat
                        igitur prefato abbati eiusque successoribus prefatam abbaciam regulariter
                        regentibus ipsum monasterium cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus rebus, quo
                        legitimo modo voluerint tractare, omnium personarum contradictione remota.
                            <rs key="#Exemption">Nullus itaque dux, marchio, comes, vicecomes,
                            archiepiscopus, episcopus nullaque magna vel parva persona predictum
                            venerabilem locum vel rectores eius de aliquibus rebus aut functionibus
                            sibi pertinentibus aliquo modo inquietare sine legali iudicio
                            presumat</rs>. Si quis vero quod absit huius nostre preceptionis
                        imperialis pariterque mundiburdi violator existat, auri obtimi mille
                        librarum pondus se compositurum agnoscat, medietatem nostre camere et
                        medietatem predicti cenobii utilitati. Quod ut verius credatur cauciusque
                        custodiatur, hanc paginam manu propria roborantes inferius iussimus
                        sigillari. Signum domni Chuonradi serenissimi et invictissimi imperatoris
                        augusti. Kadelohus cancellarius vice Herimanni archicancellarii recognovit.
                        Datum XIIII kal. mad. anno dominice incarnationis millesimo XXXVII,
                        indictione V, anno autem domni Chuonradi regnantis [X]IIII, imperii [X]I.
                        Actum Ravenne; feliciter amen.</ab>
